title: Teacher Appreciation Donations
description: Hello UHS Parents. Fall is officially upon us, and this is a long academic stretch for our students and teachers. Annually, the UHS administrative team hosts a Fall Teacher Appreciation Luncheon. We would love to include a few appreciation items from our parents. If you would like to participate, we are asking for a donation of gift cards or gift certificates. We appreciate your willingness to make a donation and will gladly follow up with a donation letter, which includes our Tax ID Number and donation value. If you have any questions or would like more information, please contact Yvette Sanchez or Ellie Palomo, or you may deliver donations to the UHS Office by Monday, October 24, 2022. THANK YOU FOR YOUR SUPPORT! Yvette Sanchez, 559-278-1589, yvettesanchez@mail.fresnostate.edu Ellie Palomo, 559-278-1114, epalomo@mail.fresnostate.edu
